<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="587" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,158,1042]" pageId="8" pageNumber="587">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,981,1006]" pageId="8" pageNumber="587">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species name refers to the appearance of the gryllacridid and the female subgenital plate. From Latin, bellus = cute.
</paragraph>
